headline: Arista Holds Key Chart Level After AI Stock Dips From All-Time High
summary: Arista Networks is holding support at its 21-day exponential moving average, and a rebound from that level could provide a follow-on entry.  A positive reaction to earnings in August was followed by a sell-off during its analyst day in September.  For the current quarter, Arista projected sales of $2.25 billion at the midpoint, slightly above views of $2.12 billion.
